<node id="E客戶">
  <data key="d0">E客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">E客戶 is an organization that receives and undergoes various maintenance services, particularly related to their Splunk system. Detailed records of these maintenance activities are meticulously documented and stored by the relevant authorities or service providers. E客戶 serves as a client entity for whom comprehensive maintenance support is provided, ensuring all interactions and services are thoroughly recorded. The descriptions consistently emphasize that E klientów not only receive regular maintenance but also undergo specific maintenance work on designated dates such as 2025/11/14. These records encompass multiple aspects of the maintenance process, including on-site work and continuous service documentation, ensuring a complete and accurate history of all maintenance activities performed for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a customer for whom maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is an organization for which maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client entity for whom maintenance activities are recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is the client for whom maintenance records are kept.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-738a58105cbf665748b3257e0cfee9ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58</data>
