  <data key="d3">chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345e520afd2a192e25824abb33740d46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-886b4b629f3088ef8656c792cf7b3e8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b</data>
  <data key="d2">World Athletics Federation, also known as World Athletics, is a governing body that oversees global athletics competitions and record validations. It plays a crucial role in managing various competitions, including the World Athletics Championships, ensuring compliance with rules and regulations for these events. The organization's responsibilities extend to validating records set by athletes during these competitions, thereby maintaining the integrity of athletic achievements through rigorous validation processes.

World Athletics Federation ensures that all global athletics competitions adhere to standardized guidelines, contributing significantly to the fair and organized conduct of international sports events. It oversees a range of activities, from managing major championships like the World Athletics Championships to validating new records set by athletes worldwide. This organization is dedicated to upholding the highest standards in athletics, ensuring that every event it governs operates under consistent and transparent rules.

Through its comprehensive oversight, World Athletics Federation supports the global athletics community by fostering a competitive yet fair environment for athletes from around the world to showcase their talents.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees global athletics events like the World Athletics Championship.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
