<node id="B客戶">
  <data key="d0">B客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B客户 is an organization that serves as the subject of detailed maintenance records. These records are systematically maintained and updated by various parties responsible for overseeing B客户的 upkeep and service needs, emphasizing its role in receiving services whose activities are meticulously documented. The documentation process ensures that all relevant information regarding the maintenance history, current status, and future requirements of B客户 is consistently recorded and preserved. This entity is explicitly referred to as a client or customer in multiple descriptions, highlighting its central position in receiving services for which comprehensive records are kept by oversight parties. Maintenance records for B客户 are uniformly maintained by different entities to ensure that all pertinent information concerning the organization's maintenance needs and history remains accessible and up-to-date.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef</data>
