<node id="FISAC資料收容-進行中">
  <data key="d0">FISAC資料收容-進行中</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The FISAC data containment procedure is ongoing, involving IP application submission requests via API to FISAC.&lt;SEP&gt;A process currently ongoing to handle FISAC data containment.&lt;SEP&gt;#fisac資料收容是B部門正在處理的任務之一，涉及API IP申請。&lt;SEP&gt;FISAC資料收容-進行中refers to ongoing work involving the submission of IP application forms for API usage to FISAC.&lt;SEP&gt;This event describes the ongoing process of data collection for FISAC, involving an IP address application request to be submitted by james.&lt;SEP&gt;FISAC data collection task that has been initiated but remains unfinished.&lt;SEP&gt;FISAC資料收容-進行中refers to ongoing efforts by B部門to collect FISAC data using API IP application requests submitted by James.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6</data>
