  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Centos作業系統升級(評估中), also known as the CentOS operating system upgrade evaluation, is an ongoing and pending task aimed at assessing and planning the update of CentOS system components. This task involves evaluating various aspects related to upgrading the CentOS operating systems, which are currently in progress and scheduled for evaluation and implementation. The primary objective is to ensure a comprehensive assessment of the necessary steps required for the successful upgrade of CentOS systems, thereby ensuring that all system components will be updated accordingly. The Centos作業系統升級(評估中) remains an active task, with multiple assessments underway to determine the feasibility and impact of the upgrade on existing systems.</data>
