<node id="C客戶">
  <data key="d0">C客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">C客戶 is a customer entity or organization for which maintenance records are maintained. These descriptions consistently indicate that C客戶 refers to a client whose interactions, particularly related to maintenance services, are documented and recorded comprehensively. The maintenance records encompass both past and ongoing service activities, ensuring a detailed history of the relationship between C客戶 and the service provider. This includes various forms of maintenance such as work conducted, activities performed, and services being provided. C客户是一家接受维护服务的公司，进一步证实了C客戶是一个接受维护服务的企业实体。&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the client for whom maintenance work was performed.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is a client for whom maintenance records are kept, involving Splunk SIEM system maintenance.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is a client for whom maintenance records are kept.</data>
