<edge source="E客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">15.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人员, E客户) refers to a relationship where C人员 is responsible for providing comprehensive maintenance and support services on behalf of E客户. This includes various activities aimed at ensuring the smooth operation and efficient functioning of E客户的 systems, particularly focusing on addressing technical issues and conducting necessary maintenance tasks.

Specifically, C人员 serves as the designated handling engineer who performs maintenance work related to E客户的 operations. For instance, C人员 has conducted maintenance tasks and provided support services for E客户's Splunk system, demonstrating a specialized focus on this technology. The responsibilities of C人员 encompass a wide range of activities including conducting specified maintenance tasks, recording maintenance activities, and addressing any technical issues that may arise.

E客戶 receives these maintenance services from C人員 to ensure the continuous operational readiness and efficiency of their systems. This relationship underscores a collaborative effort between C人员 and E客户 to maintain optimal system performance and address any challenges efficiently. Maintenance support provided by C人员 includes both on-site work and specialized service for technologies such as Splunk, indicating a tailored approach to meet E客户的 specific needs.

Several instances have been documented where C人員 has provided maintenance services to E客戶, including a notable case on 2025/11/14. These interactions highlight the ongoing nature of the relationship between C人员 and E客户, emphasizing continuous support and collaboration to ensure that E客户的 systems remain well-maintained and operational at all times.</data>
  <data key="d9">client relationship,client-engineer,client-engineer relationship,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,record keeping,responsibility,service maintenance,service provider,service provision,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380</data>
