<edge source="Noah Carter" target="World Athletics Federation">
  <data key="d7">36.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Noah Carter, in relation to the World Athletics Federation (WAF), is a prominent athlete whose achievements are closely monitored and validated by this international organization. The WAF plays a critical role in overseeing the rules, regulations, and validation processes for international athletic competitions, ensuring that athletes like Noah Carter adhere strictly to established criteria and standards.

The federation is responsible for validating record-breaking performances such as Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record through rigorous procedures. This ensures that all records set by athletes meet the necessary requirements to maintain the integrity of athletic achievements. The WAF not only monitors championship events where new records are established but also guarantees ongoing compliance with rules during competitions.

Furthermore, the World Athletics Federation governs the competitions in which Noah Carter participates and validates his records, ensuring strict adherence to regulations and standards set for global athletics. It oversees the validation process of all athletic achievements and specifically focuses on world-record-breaking performances like those accomplished by Noah Carter. The WAF ensures that the rules and regulations under which Noah Carter competes are strictly followed and maintained, upholding the fairness and credibility of international athletic events.

Additionally, the World Athletics Federation validates records set at competitions such as the World Athletics Championship where athletes like Noah Carter break new barriers. It oversees record validations for performances in championship settings, supporting athlete achievements through rigorous validation processes to ensure the legitimacy and integrity of these milestones. The WAF also regulates the rules and guidelines under which athletes participate in events like Noah Carter's record-breaking race, ensuring that all participants comply with governance standards during championship events.

Overall, the World Athletics Federation plays a crucial role in validating and regulating records set by athletes like Noah Carter at major championships, supporting their achievements while maintaining the highest level of integrity and fairness within international athletics.</data>
  <data key="d9">athlete governance,athlete oversight,athlete recognition,athlete regulation,athlete supervision,athletic achievement,athletic governance,governance,governing body,oversight,record validation,regulation,validation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5</data>
