<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) denotes a professional relationship where B人员 (personnel) provides comprehensive maintenance services and technical support to C客户 (customer). This relationship involves the personnel handling various maintenance tasks related to systems or equipment belonging to the customer. The responsibilities of B人员 include both proactive measures such as record-keeping and reactive actions like addressing issues that arise during operation.

B人员's role encompasses providing on-site service, record-keeping, and problem-solving aimed at maintaining optimal performance for C客户的 equipment or systems. This includes both scheduled maintenance tasks and handling unexpected problems to ensure ongoing operational efficiency. B人员 maintains a direct working relationship with the customer, ensuring that all necessary tasks are completed as required according to the specific needs of the customer.

B人员 provides these services specifically in relation to Splunk驻点服务 (Splunk on-site service) for C客户. For example, B人员 was assigned to perform maintenance tasks related to this service on October 13, 2025. This role involves both scheduled and unscheduled maintenance activities aimed at ensuring the proper functioning of the customer’s systems or equipment.

In summary, (B人员, C客户) represents a professional relationship where B人员's main responsibility is to provide tailored maintenance services and technical support for C客户的 Splunk SIEM system and other related tasks. The personnel work closely with the customer to address any issues promptly and maintain optimal operational efficiency through comprehensive service provisions.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員provided maintenance support to C客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">client relationship,client-engineer relationship,engineer responsibility,engineer-client interaction,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,responsibility,service delivery,service provider,service provision,technical support</data>
